<Pnumber>31</Pnumber>
<P1para>
<Text>An award of universal credit is to include an amount in respect of childcare costs (“the childcare costs element”) in respect of an assessment period in which the claimant meets both—</Text>
<P3 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2013/376/regulation/31/a" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/regulation/31/a" id="regulation-31-a">
<Pnumber>a</Pnumber>
<P3para>
<Text>the work condition (see regulation 32); and</Text>
</P3para>
</P3>
<P3 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2013/376/regulation/31/b" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/regulation/31/b" id="regulation-31-b">
<Pnumber>b</Pnumber>
<P3para>
<Text>the childcare costs condition (see regulation 33).</Text>
</P3para>
</P3>
</P1para>
</P1></P1group></Pblock></Part></Body></Secondary></Legislation>